2^{-t}\binom{t}{t/2}=\frac{t!}{2^t((t/2)!)^2}\sim \frac{\sqrt{2\pi t}t^te^{2\cdot t/2}}{2^t\cdot 2\pi (t/2)(t/2)^{2\cdot t/2}e^t}=\sqrt{2\pi/t}
P_x(t):=\frac{t+x}{2}!\frac{t-x}{2}!-((t/2)!)^2
\binom{t}{\frac{t+x}{2}}=\frac{t!}{\frac{t+x}{2}!\frac{t-x}{2}!}=\frac{t!}{((t/2)!)^2+P_x(t)}\sim \frac{t!}{((t/2)!)^2}=\binom{t}{t/2}
